Predictions: Women’s race tight but I’m placing my bet on Vivian Cheruiyot, says LimoFormer winner advises that for an athlete to perform well in a race, it’s not about training only, but also a matter of good calculations, says this years’ edition is a little bit tricky because the athletes will race in 19 clockwise laps of 2.15 kilometres on a circuit course